  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Halloween Picket Maze</i> is a real-time puzzle game where you play a cat trying to find her way home. Avoid ghosts, trick hounds and dodge catapulting pumpkins. With 60 levels this is a short Halloween game to tickle your gray cells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh and there are poems!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137550/extras/acce83f3e09094d3059a52d2d76643db.avif?t=1729876233\" width=618 height=93 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  Flying broom, a witch's hat.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    In this game, you play a cat.  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  Scary pumpkins, ghosts shine bright.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    Pass the levels, have no fright.  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  Hop through fences, outsmart them all.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    This cat is clever, you'll have a ball.  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  Avoid large hounds, ghost and the rest.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    To beat this game, these you must best.  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  Be good at moving, and thinking too.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    Don't get scared, when ghosts go <i>WHOOO!</i>  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  If <i>trick-or-treating</i>, you find lame.  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    Sit down and play, this Halloween game.  </ul></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137550/extras/d90fdc63a7544722eacc9593d563c41d.avif?t=1729876233\" width=618 height=94 /></span></p>",
